Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.75,0:00:05.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桥断了……
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.99,0:00:08.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就没法去玛陵德了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.58,0:00:11.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师 能不能争取把药送过去……
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.79,0:00:15.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是水流这么湍急 想坐船过去都不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.02,0:00:24.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉莎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.20,0:00:29.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么宽的河
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.63,0:00:31.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定能有地方迂回过去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.17,0:00:32.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.62,0:00:36.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得尽快赶到玛陵德去！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.85,0:00:43.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾德娜……
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.36,0:00:46.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.95,0:00:53.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可别忘了要救我哥哥的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.85,0:00:55.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 当然不会忘！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.06,0:01:02.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史雷……
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.84,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.00,0:02:36.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是你要去罗兰斯的理由？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.36,0:02:38.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很奇怪吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.67,0:02:39.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.89,0:02:42.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是觉得这理由够粗率的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
